’Ł@aa48bd6585a71d5e3de8dfa5fc7e3cb0682b3f0e8bb9517109ca8f3c912df04dŁÄTitle: title: detect type
Path: Flags
Content:
``--prefer-filesize, -f``
: For ints display them as human-readable file sizes.
``--prefer-dmy``
: Prefer day-month-year format for ambiguous dates.
