’Ł@cd973fa22ba828b6c0c822ed716895316e38cf996b5e513784fed8d7a4274329ŚŪTitle: title: detect type
Path: Examples
Content:
Bool from string
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'true' | detect type
true

```
Bool is case insensitive
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'FALSE' | detect type
false

```
Int from plain digits
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '42' | detect type
42

```
Int with underscores
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '1_000_000' | detect type
1000000

```
Int with commas
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '1,234,567' | detect type
1234567

```
Float from decimal
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '3.14' | detect type
3.14

```
Float in scientific notation
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '6.02e23' | detect type
601999999999999995805696.0

```
Prefer filesize for ints
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '1024' | detect type -f
1.0 kB

```
Date Y-M-D
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '2022-01-01' | detect type
Sat, 1 Jan 2022 00:00:00 +0800 (4 years ago)

```
Date with time and offset
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '2022-01-01T00:00:00Z' | detect type
Sat, 1 Jan 2022 00:00:00 +0000 (4 years ago)

```
Date D-M-Y
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '31-12-2021' | detect type
Fri, 31 Dec 2021 00:00:00 +0800 (4 years ago)

```
Date M-D-Y (default for ambiguous)
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '01/02/2025' | detect type
Thu, 2 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0800 (a year ago)

```
Prefer DMY for ambiguous dates
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '01/02/2025' | detect type --prefer-dmy
Sat, 1 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0800 (a year ago)

```
Unknown stays a string
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'not-a-number' | detect type
not-a-number

```
